<div id="title">Special Financing</div>
<center><img style="padding-bottom: 10px;" src="res/images/_accents/divider-simple.png" alt="-----"></center>
<p>On approved credit you can finance your flooring, cabinetry, countertop, and window covering purchases from Vallejo Floor Company and spread out your payments <span style="font-weight: bold;">with absolutely no finance charges</span> if you pay your balance in full within twelve months.</p>
<p>For our customers with limited or less-than-perfect credit histories we also offer a flexible in-house payment plan that can allow you to finance your purchase with simple qualification requirements and <span style="font-weight: bold;">no credit check</span>.</p>
